name: Charitas
additional_notices: Kindly be aware that liquidity provided in Automated Market Maker platforms (eg. Uniswap, Sushiswap, Balancer) can be removed (also known as rug pulling), resulting in a collapse of available liquidity. Please exercise caution when trading! This notice is NOT directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder for our users.

description.en:
Charitas is a community-driven protocol that is revolutionizing the way we fund charities. Our native token is built with simple tokenomics: static rewards, charity donations, automatic LP, and token burns. Investing in Charitas allows holders to govern our upcoming donation platform. Charitas is designed with real-world purpose to ensure the longevity and growth of the protocol. 

In development: Charitas Voting Application, NFT Marketplace, Charitas Foundation and Charitas Launchpad.
